```plantuml
@startuml gabrielfarah_OpenHub

package "OpenHub System" {
    [GitHub API] as github
    [RabbitMQ] as rabbitmq
    [MongoDB] as mongodb

    component "Crawler" {
        [crawler.py] as crawler
    }

    component "Worker Manager" {
        [manager.py] as manager
    }

    package "Analysis Modules" {
        component "Security" {
            [code_linter/main.py] as security_linter
            [basic_security/main.py] as basic_security
        }

        component "Testability" {
            [cyclomatic_complexity/main.py] as testability
        }

        component "Reusability" {
            [maintainability_index/main.py] as reusability
            [coupling_analyzer/main.py] as coupling
        }

        component "Usability" {
            [documentation_analysis/main.py] as docs
            [popularity_index/main.py] as popularity
        }
    }

    [Configuration Files] as config
}

github --> crawler : Fetches repo data
crawler --> mongodb : Stores metadata
crawler --> rabbitmq : Publishes tasks
rabbitmq --> manager : Consumes tasks
manager --> "Analysis Modules" : Executes tests
"Analysis Modules" --> mongodb : Stores results

config --> crawler : Provides settings
config --> manager : Provides settings
config --> "Analysis Modules" : Provides settings

@enduml
```